<div class='homepage-container container'>

  <%= image_tag "https://res.cloudinary.com/duw2hqlo3/image/upload/v1576435064/grammar_blitz_full_logo_fjjnmv.png", alt: "grammar-blitz logo", id:"logo-home"%>

  <div class="grammar-god">
    <%= image_tag "https://res.cloudinary.com/duw2hqlo3/image/upload/v1576600682/output_crop_ivm9fy.gif", alt: "German God of Grammar"%>
    <h3 class="over px-3">Practice your cases with 10.000+ sentences and join the German Gods of Grammar.</h3>
  </div>

  <div class="home-content py-5">
    <%= link_to "LET'S GET THE FUN STARTED!",  exercices_path, {:class=>'home-button'} %>

    <div class="cool-border"></div>

    <h2 class='mt-5 mb-5'>Grammar Blitz?! Was ist das denn?!</h2>

    <div class="container mb-5">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12">
          <p><i class="landing-icon fas fa-atom"></i></p>
          <h3>German is Hard</h3>
          <p>German grammar is complex. There is many rules and few chances to practice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12">
          <p><i class="landing-icon fas fa-robot"></i></p>
          <h3>The sentence machine</h3>
          <p>Grammar Blitz generate sentences randomly. You never see exactly the same sentence and are always force to find the right answer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12">
          <p><i class="landing-icon fas fa-rocket"></i></p>
          <h3>Be done already!</h3>
          <p>Practice your grammar in different context until it is second nature.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%= link_to "Sign up Sofort!",  new_user_registration_path, {:class=>'home-button'} %>
  </div>
</div>
